    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "ATIANTA\n~\nDELTA AIR LINES",
      "ATLANTA\nThe traditional Southern Belle is fast being replaced by the modern\nMiss Atlanta, a metropolis of over a million people. A major financial,\ncommercial and convention center, Atlanta also boasts of excellent\nhotels, airport motels, the Cyclorama, Stone Mountain, gay nightlife.\nDelta's Big Jets serve Atlanta from the four corners of the compass. A\nnetwork of other Delta routes makes Atlanta the Air Hub of the South-\neast. Call Delta or see your Travel Agent.\nDELTA —ONE OF AMERICA'S PIONEER SCHEDULED AIRLINES\nPOST CARD\n2015.166.2517"
    ],
